00:33:17,603 --> 00:33:18,956
Hurry! It's coming!

558
00:33:20,797 --> 00:33:22,561
Come on. We got to go.

559
00:33:22,763 --> 00:33:24,470
Get out of there! Move it!

560
00:33:30,761 --> 00:33:32,353
Get out of the way!

561
00:34:14,636 --> 00:34:15,988
1206 to dispatch. Over.

