590
00:35:13,683 --> 00:35:15,198
You're telling me
it's under power?

591
00:35:15,361 --> 00:35:17,116
Get in the goddamn siding.

592
00:35:18,401 --> 00:35:20,473
1206, stand by.

593
00:35:25,555 --> 00:35:28,279
1206. If you're going for it.
