598
00:35:35,558 --> 00:35:36,670
I know what
the hell I'm doing.

599
00:35:36,757 --> 00:35:38,751
Bullshit! You're going to
get us killed. Hey!

600
00:35:39,356 --> 00:35:41,264
1206, I need
an answer. Over.

601
00:35:43,038 --> 00:35:44,553
Realign the switch.

602
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:46,232
Over.

603
00:36:04,319 --> 00:36:07,234
The train was just going with
